item.description: That's awesome! I have been watching appbrain, but I didn't think to check the 'hot today' pages or anything like that. I checked out the' hot today' page today and we're down a ways, but we're on there! so that's pretty exciting. Thanks for the heads up Mark :).

item.title: By: Mark

item.description:
I can't help with the Market but it was listed in the Appbrain.com 'Currently hot Brain and Puzzle games' RSS Feed on April 1st!
It's a great game - I can't wait for the full version with more levels!
